<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{clientName}} - Guest Experience Platform Proposal</title>
  <style>
    @page { size: letter portrait; margin: 0.5in; }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5; color: #2d3748; background: white;
    }
    .page { width: 7.5in; margin: 0 auto 20px auto; background: white; page-break-after: always; }
    .header { padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 3px solid {{theme.accent}}; }
    .logo { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: {{theme.accent}}; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }

    .header-right { text-align: right; color: #2d3748; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }

    .client-box {
      background: {{theme.accentSoft}};
      border-left: 4px solid {{theme.accent}};
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .client-box h2 { font-size: 18px; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .client-box p { font-size: 13px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6; }

    .usd-badge {
      background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block; margin: 16px 0;
      text-align: center; width: 100%;
    }

    h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 26px; color: #2d3748; margin: 20px 0 8px 0; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #718096; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }

    .packages { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .package { border: 3px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
    .package.recommended { border-color: #2563eb; }

    .package-header { padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .package.recommended .package-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%); color: white; }
    .package:not(.recommended) .package-header { background: #f8fafc; }

    .badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .package:not(.recommended) .badge { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
    .package-name { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .package:not(.recommended) .package-name { color: #2d3748; }
    .package-price { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0; }
    .package:not(.recommended) .package-price { color: #2d3748; }
    .package-desc { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.95; }
    .package:not(.recommended) .package-desc { color: #64748b; }
    .package-body { padding: 20px; }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; color: #2d3748;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .price-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 12px;
      background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;
    }
    .price-row-label { color: #475569; }
    .price-row-value { font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; }
    .note { font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; font-style: italic; margin-top: 8px; }

    .optional-box {
      background: #fef3c7; border: 2px dashed #f59e0b; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .optional-box .section-title { color: #92400e; }

    .features-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .features-list li { padding: 6px 0 6px 20px; position: relative; font-size: 13px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.5; }
    .features-list li::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #10b981; font-weight: bold; }

    /* PAGE 2-4 */
    .content-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .content-section h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .bullet-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .bullet-list li { padding: 6px 0 6px 18px; position: relative; font-size: 13px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; }
    .bullet-list li::before { content: "•"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #64748b; }

    .info-box { background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 14px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .info-box strong { color: #1e40af; font-size: 13px; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .info-box p { color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }

    .text-section { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .text-section strong { color: #1e293b; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }

    .orange-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{theme.accent}} 0%, #FF8555 100%);
      color: white; padding: 24px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .orange-box h3 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: white; }
    .orange-box p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.95; }
    .stat-badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 12px; }

    .feature-box {
      background: white; border-left: 4px solid {{theme.accent}}; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .feature-box h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .feature-box p { font-size: 13px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }

    .arrow-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .arrow-list li { padding: 5px 0 5px 20px; position: relative; font-size: 12px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.5; }
    .arrow-list li::before { content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: {{theme.accent}}; font-weight: bold; }
    .arrow-list strong { color: #1e293b; }

    .cta-box { background: {{theme.accentSoft}}; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 24px; }
    .cta-box h4 { font-size: 15px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
    .cta-box p { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 4px; }

    @media print {
      body { print-color-adjust: exact; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- PAGE 1: PRICING -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">nutmeg</div>
    </div>

    <div class="client-box">
      <h2>Prepared For: {{clientName}}</h2>
      <p><strong>Project:</strong> Guest Experience Platform Proposal ({{verticalLabel}})</p>
      <p>Comprehensive wayfinding and AI-powered guest engagement solution tailored for {{verticalLabel}} operations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="usd-badge">ALL PRICING IN USD</div>

    <h1>Platform Packages</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Choose the solution that best enhances your guest experience</p>

    <div class="packages">
      {{!-- CARD 1: “Recommended” or left card --}}
      {{#if showBundleCards}}
        <div class="package recommended">
          <div class="package-header">
            <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
            <div class="package-name">Complete Platform</div>
            <div class="package-price">{{fmt.bundleTotal}}</div>
            <div class="package-desc">Maps ({{mapsCount}}) + AI Chatbot</div>
          </div>
          <div class="package-body">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">INTERACTIVE WAYFINDING MAPS</div>
              {{#each maps}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapBasePrice}}</span>
                </div>
              {{/each}}
              {{#ifEq mapsCount 0}}
                <div class="note">No maps added yet.</div>
              {{/ifEq}}
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">AI CHATBOT</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">IMPLEMENTATION & ONBOARDING</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">Includes training, setup, and dedicated support</div>
            </div>

            <div class="optional-box">
              <div class="section-title">OPTIONAL ADD-ONS</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Custom Illustrations</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">$1,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Additional Map Languages</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">$500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">One-time fees, pricing varies by requirements</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {{else}}
        {{#if showAiOnlyCard}}
          <div class="package recommended">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
              <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">AI CHATBOT</div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
              </div>

              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">USAGE ASSUMPTIONS</div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Conversations</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedConversations}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Cost</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedCost}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Margin Ratio</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.marginProfitRatio}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="package recommended">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">RECOMMENDED</div>
              <div class="package-name">Maps Only</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.mapsOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">Interactive map solution ({{mapsCount}} maps)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">INTERACTIVE WAYFINDING MAPS</div>
                {{#each maps}}
                  <div class="price-row">
                    <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                    <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapBasePrice}}</span>
                  </div>
                {{/each}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      {{/if}}

      {{!-- CARD 2: right card changes based on selection --}}
      {{#if showBundleCards}}
        <div class="package">
          <div class="package-header">
            <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
            <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot Only</div>
            <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
            <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
          </div>
          <div class="package-body">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">WHAT'S INCLUDED</div>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-row-label">Annual Subscription</span>
                <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="note">*Based on {{fmt.attendance}} visitors, {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} inquiry ratio, {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest</div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <div class="section-title">CORE FEATURES</div>
              <ul class="features-list">
                <li>Works in any language with automatic translation</li>
                <li>Indexed with your information as the source of truth</li>
                <li>Answers operational questions instantly</li>
                <li>Multi-channel integration (WhatsApp, Instagram, SMS)</li>
                <li>Conversation logging for insights and optimization</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {{else}}
        {{#if showMapsOnlyCard}}
          <div class="package">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
              <div class="package-name">Maps Only</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.mapsOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">Interactive map solution ({{mapsCount}} maps)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">WHAT'S INCLUDED</div>
                {{#each maps}}
                  <div class="price-row">
                    <span class="price-row-label">{{this.name}}</span>
                    <span class="price-row-value">{{../fmt.mapBasePrice}}</span>
                  </div>
                {{/each}}
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.setupFee}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">CORE FEATURES</div>
                <ul class="features-list">
                  <li>Unlimited customizable pins</li>
                  <li>Multi-language capability</li>
                  <li>Geo-fenced marketing</li>
                  <li>Guest analytics dashboard</li>
                  <li>Upsell & cross-sell tools</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="package">
            <div class="package-header">
              <div class="badge">ESSENTIAL</div>
              <div class="package-name">AI Chatbot</div>
              <div class="package-price">{{fmt.aiOnlyTotal}}</div>
              <div class="package-desc">AI-powered guest engagement</div>
            </div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div class="section-title">USAGE ASSUMPTIONS</div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">AI Usage</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiUsage}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Conversations</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedConversations}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Expected Cost</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.expectedCost}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-row">
                  <span class="price-row-label">Gross Profit (Quoted)</span>
                  <span class="price-row-value">{{fmt.aiQuotedPrice}}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 2: DETAILED FEATURES -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="content-section">
      <h3>Interactive Maps - Core Capabilities</h3>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Custom-designed interactive maps for your venue(s)</li>
        <li>Real-time attraction wait times (where applicable)</li>
        <li>Geo-fenced targeted marketing for food, retail, and special events</li>
        <li>Unlimited customizable pins for attractions, amenities, and points of interest</li>
        <li>Guest journey analytics and heat mapping</li>
        <li>Upsell and cross-sell functionality for premium experiences</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h3>AI Chatbot - Your 24/7 Digital Employee</h3>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Works in any language with automatic translation</li>
        <li>Indexed with your information as the source of truth</li>
        <li>Answers operational questions instantly: hours, pricing, policies, details</li>
        <li>Provides personalized suggestions based on guest preferences</li>
        <li>Operates 24/7 to handle guest inquiries anytime</li>
        <li>Reduces phone call volume to your staff</li>
        <li>Frees up staff to focus on in-venue guest experiences</li>
        <li>Multi-channel integration (WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, SMS)</li>
        <li>Conversation logging for insights and optimization</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>SMS Messaging:</strong>
      <p>SMS messaging fees are not included in this quote. Twilio service fees will be applied per message based on actual usage volume.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Agreement Terms</strong>
        This proposal is provided for {{clientName}}. All pricing is in US Dollars (USD) and valid for {{validityDays}} days from {{preparedDate}}.
      </div>

      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Usage Assumptions</strong>
        Pricing is based on estimated annual visitation of {{fmt.attendance}} guests with a {{fmt.inquiryRatio}} chatbot inquiry ratio and average of {{fmt.avgConvosPerGuest}} conversations per guest.
      </div>

      <div class="text-section">
        <strong>Questions About This Proposal?</strong>
        <strong>Website:</strong> www.nutmeg.io<br>
        Contact us to discuss this proposal, feature details, or implementation timeline.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 3: WHY NUTMEG -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">nutmeg</div>
    </div>

    <div class="header-right" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Proposal for: {{clientName}}</div>

    <h1>Why Nutmeg for {{clientName}}</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Purpose-built for {{verticalLabel}}s to maximize guest engagement and drive revenue opportunities</p>

    <div class="orange-box">
      <h3>Web-Based Platform = Higher Adoption</h3>
      <p>Mobile apps average less than 3% adoption. Our web-based platform achieves 50%+ adoption rates, meaning more guests engaging with your content, finding attractions faster, and making purchases.</p>
      <div class="stat-badge">17x More Guests Engaged</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Custom Interactive Wayfinding</h3>
      <p>Our design team works with you to create stunning, on-brand maps that guide guests through your venue while driving engagement with revenue-generating opportunities.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Unlimited customizable pins</strong> for attractions, amenities, and points of interest</li>
        <li><strong>Real-time updates</strong> where applicable</li>
        <li><strong>Geo-fenced marketing</strong> at the right moments</li>
        <li><strong>Upsell & cross-sell tools</strong> to promote premium experiences</li>
        <li><strong>Multi-language support</strong> (additional languages can be an extra fee)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>AI Chatbot: Your Tireless Digital Employee</h3>
      <p>More than a chatbot: an always-on team member that serves as the definitive source of truth, answering questions instantly and providing peace of mind to your guests.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Source of truth</strong> trained on your policies, hours, and offerings</li>
        <li><strong>Always on</strong> 24/7, 365 days a year</li>
        <li><strong>Answers operational questions fast</strong> like hours, pricing, policies, what to bring</li>
        <li><strong>Works in any language</strong> to reduce language barriers</li>
        <li><strong>Reduces staff workload</strong> so your team can focus on experiences</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PAGE 4: ENGAGEMENT & SUPPORT -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Maximize Guest Engagement & Revenue</h3>
      <p>{{clientName}} can benefit from increased guest engagement that drives revenue through food & beverage, retail, and premium experiences. Nutmeg is built for exactly this.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>No app download barrier</strong> every guest can access instantly via web browser</li>
        <li><strong>High adoption rate</strong> means more eyes on your revenue opportunities</li>
        <li><strong>Strategic placement</strong> promotes offers at optimal times</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics dashboard</strong> understands guest flow and engagement</li>
        <li><strong>Reduce operational costs</strong> fewer repetitive questions to staff</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Dedicated Support & Partnership</h3>
      <p>You're not just getting software: you're getting a partner committed to your success.</p>
      <ul class="arrow-list">
        <li><strong>Designated key account manager</strong> single point of contact</li>
        <li><strong>Responsive support</strong> help when you need it</li>
        <li><strong>Comprehensive onboarding</strong> training and enablement</li>
        <li><strong>Ongoing optimization</strong> continuous improvements over time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h4>Ready to Transform Guest Experience at {{clientName}}?</h4>
      <p><strong>Website:</strong> www.nutmeg.io</p>
      <p>Let's schedule a demo tailored to {{clientName}}'s needs and discuss how Nutmeg can drive engagement and revenue.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
